> "This is weird"mutered hydras "Suppostly we're in the present but if its
> that so, where the pit are the humans?"

<NEW>

HELLSCREAM looked up at HYDRAS at that question, "What humans? There
are no humans in this area. They played with technologies that were
not theirs, and went boom!" HELLSCREAM gestured with his hands as he
said boom to emphasize his point.

DIRGE GUN nodded, "There are some on one of the other continents if
you're looking for slaves." He said with a somewhat confused look on
his face. "But they're not good for anything."

SCORPONK and JHIAXUS frowned but said nothing. According to the
history that they knew humans were living and thriving in the very
tonw that they were about to use as a base.

Something was very very wrong here.

(TAG)

- Preston
